                    <msContents>
                        
                        <summary>A collection of stotras, all written by the same scribe and bound in a single volume. Each entre has a title on f. 1 in Persian script,
                        as well as an illustration.</summary>
                        <textLang mainLang="sa">Sanskrit, with additional title entries in Persian script.</textLang>

                        <msItem xml:id="Alpha_978_1">
                            <title>Gaṇeśastotra or Mahāgaṇapatistotra</title>
                            <title type="alt">گنيش سو</title>
                            <idno type="former">A.9.a.</idno>

                            <incipit> <locus>F. 1v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                oṃ namaḥ nārāyaṇāya ||
                                oṃ namaḥ gaṇeśāya namaḥ || oṃ
                                amā(r)gaṃ gataṃ karṇavakraṃ gaṇeśaṃ
                                bhutākaṃkaṇaṃ dyodhitaṃ dhūmrakenaṃ (?)
                                gale hāramuktāphalāśobhitvaritaṃ 
                                na<locus>F. 2</locus>mo jñānarūpaṃ gaṇeśaṃ namas te || 1 ||
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <explicit> <locus>F. 5</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                bhujaṃgaṃ pra<pb n="f. 5v"/>yāti paṭeyas tu muktyā (?)
                                prabhāte paṭeś caiva ekāgracitraṃ ||
                                jñeyaṃ (?) yāṃti vighnaṃ diśā śobhivaṃtaṃ ||
                                namo vighanājyaṃ gaṇeśaṃ namas te || 9 ||
                            </explicit>
                            
                            <colophon> <locus>F. 6</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                iti śrīmahāgaṇapat(i)(ye) stav(o)tra(ṃ) samāptaṃ || śubhaṃ
                            </colophon>
                            
                        </msItem> 
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="Alpha_978_2">
                            <title>Viṣṇupañjarastotra</title>
                            <title type="alt">وشن پجر</title>
                            <idno type="former">A.9.b.</idno>
                            
                            <incipit> <locus>F. 1v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                oṃ namo nārāyaṇāya ||
                                om (bra)hmapataye viṣṇupaṃjarastotramaṃtrasya nārada ṛṣi anuṣṭap chaṃdaḥ
                                śrīviṣṇuparamātmā daivatā || ahaṃ bījaṃ || so 'haṃ śa<pb n="f. 2"/>ktiḥ ||
                                aṃghrīṃ kīlakaṃ || mama sarvadeharakṣārthe jape viniyogaḥ || nāradaṛṣaye namaḥ śirasi ||
                                anuṣṭupchaṃdas namaḥ mukhe || śrīkṛṣṇa(ḥ)para<pb n="f. 2v"/>mātmādevatāyai namaḥ
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <explicit> <locus>F. 12v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                śrīviṣṇupaṃjarastotraṃ samāptam || śubham ||
                            </explicit> 
                            
                            <colophon> <locus>F. 12v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                phalaṃ prāpnuti mānavaḥ ||
                                <note>Added in later hand.</note>
                            </colophon>
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="Alpha_978_3">
                            <title>Ekaślokīrāmāyaṇa</title>
                            <title type="alt">راماين اک سلوکی</title>
                            <idno type="former">A.9.c.</idno>
                            
                            <note>See NCC, vol. 3, p. 55.</note>
                            
                            <incipit> <locus>F. 1v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                oṃ namaḥ nārāyaṇāya | 
                                oṃ atha ekaślokīrāmāyaṇaṃ || oṃ
                                    ādau rāmatapovanādigamaṇaṃ || hatvā mṛgaṃkāṃcano
                                    vaidehyāharaṇaṃ jaṭāya maraṇaṃ || sugrī<pb n="f. 2"/>vasaṃ x m<gap reason="illegible"/>
                                    vālīnirgrahaṇaṃ samudrataraṇaṃ laṃkāpurīdāhanaṃ ||
                                    paścād rāvanakuṃbhakarṇadalanaṃ || etad dhi rāmāyaṇaṃ
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <explicit> <locus>F. 2</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                iti rāmāyaṇaṃ samāptaṃ
                            </explicit> 
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="Alpha_978_4">
                            <title>Ekaślokībhāgavata</title>
                            <title type="alt">بهاگوت اک سلوکی</title>
                            <idno type="former">A.9.c.</idno>
                            
                            <note>See NCC, vol. 3, p. 55.</note>
                            
                            <incipit> <locus>F. 2v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                śrīkṛṣṇāya namaḥ || oṃ
                                ādau devakidevadehajananaṃ || gopīgṛhaṃ vardhanaṃ ||
                                māyāpūtanajīvitāpaharaṇaṃ || govardhanoddhāraṇaṃ ||
                                kaṃsacchedanakau<pb n="f. 3"/>ravādiharaṇaṃ || kuṃtīsutaḥ pālanaṃ
                                etad bhāvataṃ purānakathitaṃ || śrīkṛṣṇalīlāvṛtaṃ ||1||
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <explicit> <locus>F. 9v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                iti ekaśloke bhāgavataṃ samāptam ||
                            </explicit> 
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="Alpha_978_5">
                            <title>Śanistotra</title>
                            <title type="alt">شنی ستوتر</title>
                            <idno type="former">A.9.d.</idno>
                            
                            <incipit> <locus>F. 1v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                iti śanimaṃtraḥ śatro devī rabhyeṣṭāpe śrāpo bhavana pitaye śanyor abhya sarvan tu tān
                                oṃ namaḥ śanaiścarāya namaḥ || oṃ
                                sauraḥ śanaiścaro maṃḍo
                                yamaḥ khaṃjo mahīruhaḥ ||
                                x pāsutaśvaravittaḥ (?)
                                pātaṃgiś caṃtake namaḥ ||1||
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <explicit> <locus>F. 3v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript  -->
                                <note>It ends on f. 3v, which is missing from the microfilm</note>
                            </explicit> 
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="Alpha_978_6">
                            <title>Mahimnaḥpārastotra</title>
                            <title type="alt">مهمنان</title>
                            <idno type="former">A.9.e.</idno>
                            
                            <note>The beginning is identical with that of the <title>Mahimnaḥstotra</title> of <persName key="person_128612988">Puṣpadanta</persName>; see B.11.t.</note>
                            
                            <incipit> <locus>F. 1v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                oṃ namaḥ śivāya || oṃ mahimnaḥpārate paramavidvaṣoyadyasadṛśī ||
                                stutir v(b)ramhādīnām api tadavasannās tv api giraḥ ||
                                athāvācyaḥ sarvāḥ sumatipari <pb n="f. 2"/> ṇāmāvadhigṛṇan mamāpy eṣa stotre
                                haranirapavādaḥ parakaraḥ || 1 ||
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <explicit> <locus>F. 27</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                iti mahimnaḥpārastotraṃ samāptaṃ ||
                            </explicit> 
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="Alpha_978_7">
                            <title>Śanināmāni</title>
                            <title type="alt">گنئشا</title>
                            <idno type="former">A.9.f.</idno>
                            
                            <note>The <title>Saptaślokīmālā</title> or <title>Saptaślokīgītā</title> in 8 verses, following mantras; the matras are found in <idno>G.iii.c.XIV</idno>.</note>
                            
                            <incipit> <locus>F. 1v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                oṃ namo nārāyaṇāya || oṃ asya śrīsaptaslok<supplied reason="omitted">e</supplied> mālāmaṃtrasya śrībhagavān vedavyāsa ṛṣiḥ anuṣṭ(u)pchanda
                                śrīkṛṣṇaḥ paramātmā devatā || oṃm ity ekākṣaraṃ v(b)rahma iti <pb n="f. 2"/> maṃtraḥ ||
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <incipit> <note>The verses begin here.</note>
                                <locus>F. 4v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                śrībhagavān uvāca ||
                                vyāharaṃ māme anusmaran ||
                                yaḥ prayāti tyajaṃ(n)dehaṃ
                                sa yāti paramāṃ gatiṃ ||1||
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <explicit> <locus>F. 7v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                iti śrīsaptaślokī<pb n="F. 8"/>gītā samāptaṃ ||
                                śubhaṃ sarvajagatāṃ ||
                            </explicit> 
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="Alpha_978_8">
                            <title>Viṣṇusahasranāma</title>
                            <title type="alt">وشن سهسرنام</title>
                            <idno type="former">A.9.g.</idno>
                            
                            <note>The <title>Viṣṇusahasranāma</title>, allegedly from the Janadharma in the Uttamānuśāsana of the Śāntiparvan of the <title key="work_181826247">Mahābhārata</title>.
                            (I do not find it in the Śāntiparvan); 63 verses.</note>
                            
                            <incipit> <locus>F. 1v</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                oṃ namo nārāyaṇāya || oṃ
                                yasya smaraṇame ātreṇa
                                tatsamaṃ sārabaṃdhanāt ||
                                vimucyate namas tasmai
                                viṣṇave prabha viṣṇave ||
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <explicit> <locus>F. 62</locus>
                                <!-- transcript -->
                                iti iti mahābhārate śāṃtiparvaṇi uttamānuśāsan ja(?)nadha<pb n="F. 62v"/>rme su(?)śrīviṣṇunāmasahasrasa(mā)m(pt)|
                                śubhaṃ ||
                            </explicit> 
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
                        
